{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775848048369,"sessionID":"ses_28735da7cffeKZi0BV2UsN2PY9","part":{"id":"prt_d78cabad6001FZNJZKMhe6pqTH","messageID":"msg_d78cab29e001ILouvxTjKb5LEE","sessionID":"ses_28735da7cffeKZi0BV2UsN2PY9","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_4f5444f9db064c0f8890bd45","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-009/README.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-009/README.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-009 — Router HTTP 反向代理核心\n2: \n3: **Module:** pkg/router  \n4: **Language:** Go  \n5: **Size:** M\n6: \n7: ## Summary\n8: \n9: Implement HTTP reverse proxy core functionality for the pkg/router module.\n10: \n11: ## Status\n12: \n13: - [ ] Scaffold directory structure\n14: - [ ] Design reverse proxy architecture\n15: - [ ] Implement proxy core logic\n16: - [ ] Add routing rules engine\n17: - [ ] Add connection pooling\n18: - [ ] Add health checks\n19: - [ ] Add unit tests\n20: - [ ] Add integration tests\n21: \n22: ## Notes\n23: \n24: See `notes/` directory for implementation notes and decisions.\n25: \n26: ## Source Files\n27: \n28: See `src/` directory for source code changes.\n\n(End of file - total 28 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-009 — Router HTTP 反向代理核心\n\n**Module:** pkg/router  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** M\n\n## Summary\n\nImplement HTTP reverse proxy core functionality for the pkg/router module.\n\n## Status\n\n- [ ] Scaffold directory structure\n- [ ] Design reverse proxy architecture\n- [ ] Implement proxy core logic\n- [ ] Add routing rules engine\n- [ ] Add connection pooling\n- [ ] Add health checks\n- [ ] Add unit tests\n- [ ] Add integration tests","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-009/R